#  Task Management App (MERN Stack)

A modern **Task Management Web Application** built with the **MERN stack** â€” featuring authentication, CRUD operations, filters, sorting, pagination, and smooth UI animations.  
This project allows users to manage their daily tasks efficiently with a clean and interactive interface.

---

##  Features

###  Authentication
- **Signup & Login** with **JWT (JSON Web Token)** authentication  
- Secure cookies  
 

###  Task Management
- **Create**, **Read**, **Update**, and **Delete** tasks  
- Edit task title, description, completion status, and tags  
- Tasks stored and retrieved via **MongoDB Atlas**  

###  Filters & Sorting
- Filter tasks by **tags**
- Sort tasks by **status** (complete / incomplete)
- **Pagination** support for large task lists

### UI & UX
- Built with **Tailwind CSS** + **Material UI (MUI)** for modern, responsive design  
- **Framer Motion** for smooth transitions and animations  
- **React Icons** and **React Spinners** for enhanced visual feedback  

---

##  Tech Stack

Frontend:
React.js, Tailwind CSS, Material UI (MUI), Framer Motion

Backend:
Node.js, Express.js

Database:
MongoDB (with Mongoose ODM)

Authentication:
JWT (JSON Web Token)

Deployment:
**Frontend:** [Vercel Deployment Link](https://task-management-app-cyan-one.vercel.app)  
**Backend:** [Render API Link](https://your-backend-api.onrender.com)



